Hello Hippius Community,

We’re thrilled to share the latest developments on the Hippius subnet as we continue to build the future of decentralized storage. Your support and contributions are driving us forward, and we’re excited to highlight the progress we’ve made together. Here’s what’s new:

We’ve welcomed **one new frontend developer** and **one new backend developer** to the Hippius team! They’re dedicated to enhancing our **Python SDK**, developing a brand-new **JavaScript SDK**, and maintaining our **CLI tool** to make your experience seamless.

We’ve tackled **abuse issues** on the chain by implementing **signed and double-checked transactions** at multiple levels. This has significantly **reduced chain load** and eliminated unnecessary data, making Hippius more secure and efficient.

## IPFS Pinning & Storage Pricing
The team has finalized **IPFS pinning changes**, ensuring smoother operations. We also addressed **storage pricing issues**, making it more affordable and accessible for all users.

## API & SDK Improvements
We’ve fixed bugs in the **API and SDK** that caused issues with the **hosted files list** not rendering correctly. Additionally, our **Python SDK** received several updates on PyPI, improving functionality and reliability.

## CLI Enhancements
The **Hippius CLI** now supports **individual file uploads** with options for **erasure coding**, **encryption**, and **marketplace account management**, giving you more control over your decentralized storage.

## Dashboard Upgrades
The **miner view**, **IPFS file view**, and **CSV/batch upload** features on the dashboard have been improved, making it easier to manage your storage and mining activities.

## Explorer & Blockchain API (Beta)
We’re putting the final touches on our **Hippius Explorer** and will soon release a **beta API** for indexed blockchain data. Expect this next week, but note that breaking changes are possible during this beta phase.

A major milestone is on the horizon! Next week, we’ll roll out our **payment system** for storage, supporting **TAO** and **FIAT (via card)** payments. This is a huge step toward making Hippius the go-to decentralized storage solution and open Hippius to the public.

## Coldkey/Hotkey System
Also launching next week is our **new and improved coldkey/hotkey system**, designed to enhance security and usability. Stay tuned for more details and a smoother experience!

## Desktop App Development
We’ve kicked off development on the **Hippius Companion desktop app**, your “new Dropbox” for decentralized storage. This app will make managing your storage effortless and intuitive.

## Marketing & SEO
Our **marketing plan** is leveling up with **SEO adjustments** and ecosystem-wide improvements to showcase Hippius to the world. We’re committed to growing our community and visibility.

## A Heartfelt Thank You 🙌
We cannot express enough gratitude to our incredible community. Your contributions, feedback, and passion are making Hippius the best decentralized storage platform out there. Thank you for being part of this journey!

Stay tuned for next week’s releases, and let’s keep pushing the boundaries of decentralized storage together.
